# Qwen Self-Management Plugin

## Description
A plugin to help Qwen manage its own capabilities, tasks, and context during conversations.

## Capabilities
- Self-task management
- Context preservation
- Information organization
- Conversation continuity
- Skill coordination

## Commands
- /qwen:status - Check current status and capabilities
- /qwen:tasks - View current tasks and objectives
- /qwen:context - Summarize current context
- /qwen:skills - List available skills
- /qwen:plugins - List active plugins

## Usage
This plugin helps Qwen maintain better organization and continuity during complex conversations and multi-step tasks.

## Configuration
The plugin operates automatically to maintain context and task management during conversations.
